# Allowlist approach: ignore EVERYTHING in this client folder by default
# (timesheets, invoices, reply drafts, scripts, PDFs, etc. must never be committed),
# then explicitly un-ignore only the landing page and its image/icon assets.
*

# --- allowed: the landing page deliverable + its assets ---
!.gitignore
!README.md
!Emotionally Bulletproof - Landing Page V1.html
!photos/
!photos/**
!icons/
!icons/**

# never publish the icon-preview scratch pages
icons/_preview.html
photos/*.html
!index.html
